page.title: 10THE MILL,COMMERCIAL END
page.content: At the bottom of Mill Lane down Commercial End there is a mill. It has now stopped working. It has been there for many years and has provided lots of jobs for villagers.There have been talks of knocking it down and building houses.Lots of people don't want this to happen.Many people down Mill Lane think it is a good idea because it blocks out the sun.There has been a list of names to see who doesn't want it knocked down and it has been sent off to a person who wants to know about it.I think that it has been decided that it will be demolished but I and many other people hope not.
